[Sources]
  StackCheckLibCommon.c

[Sources.IA32]
  IA32/CheckCookieMsvc.nasm | MSFT

[Sources.X64]
  X64/CheckCookieMsvc.nasm | MSFT

[Sources.IA32, Sources.X64]
  IA32/StackCookieInterrupt.nasm

[Sources.ARM]
  Arm/StackCookieInterrupt.S |GCC

[Sources.AARCH64]
  AArch64/StackCookieInterrupt.S |GCC

